---
By: Annamalai Swami
Locus:
  Page: 116
  Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Ego
---
The ego is just like a ghost. It has no real form of its own.
...Identifying oneself with the body and mind results in ignorance of the
Self. This is how the ego takes birth. Detaching ourselves and disengaging
from the body and the mind results in the death of the ego.
